It uses Groq‚Äôs LLM (e.g., Gemma2-9b-It) for answering questions with detailed and context-aware responses, and sentence-transformer embeddings with ChromaDB for efficient semantic search.

items.name: CANES
items.description: Medical image segmentation remains a crucial challenge in automated cardiac diagnosis. We present the CANES-Net architecture, a novel architecture combining U-Net with Transformer attention, Mamba selective state-space modeling with class-specific loss functions to improve multi-class cardiac structure segmentation on the ACDC dataset.
